OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782751677
OL,3,CTwo jailed after fraudulent refunds
OL,4,Cworth half-a-million uncovered
OL,6,FTwo men have been jailed in Portsmouth
OL,7,Ffor a series of fraud, theft and money
OL,8,Flaundering offences targeting small
OL,9,Fbusinesses.
OL,11,FYusef Tourino, aged 28 and George
OL,12,FCampion, aged 25, both of no fixed
OL,13,Fabode, were sentenced at Portsmouth
OL,14,FCrown Court.
OL,16,FIt follows an investigation by the
OL,17,FSouth East Organised Crime Unit
OL,18,F(SEROCU) which uncovered nearly half-a-
OL,19,Fmillion pounds in fraudulent refunds.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
