PN,38802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782751677
OL,3,CTwo jailed after fraudulent refunds
OL,4,Cworth half-a-million uncovered
OL,6,FFrom November 2023 until November
OL,7,F2025, Tourino travelled to locations
OL,8,Facross England and Wales, committing
OL,9,Fover 64 frauds and two thefts on a
OL,10,Fvariety of small businesses such as
OL,11,Fvet surgeries and hotels, reaching
OL,12,Fover 22 different counties, including
OL,13,FKent and Hampshire.
OL,15,FDuring March 2024, Campion assisted
OL,16,FTourino in carrying out a number of
OL,17,Ffraud's and thefts on small businesses
OL,18,Facross Nottingham and Llandudno.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
