CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782751677
OL,3,CTwo jailed after fraudulent refunds
OL,4,Cworth half-a-million uncovered
OL,6,FAs part of his offending, Tourino used
OL,7,Fstolen card details to purchase goods,
OL,8,Fmanipulating transaction values to
OL,9,Fincrease the amounts charged. He would
OL,10,Fthen request refunds to accounts under
OL,11,Fhis control.
OL,13,FUpon his arrest in November 2025,
OL,14,FTourino was found in possession of a
OL,15,Fnumber of high-value items including
OL,16,Fclothing and mobile phones. Analysis
OL,17,Fof his bank accounts showed he
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782751677
OL,3,CTwo jailed after fraudulent refunds
OL,4,Cworth half-a-million uncovered
OL,6,FAt a hearing in Portsmouth Crown Court
OL,7,Fon 22 April, Tourino pleaded guilty to
OL,8,F64 counts of fraud, 2 counts of theft
OL,9,Fand 3 counts of money laundering
OL,10,Famounting to #462,000.
OL,12,FTourino was sentenced to five years
OL,13,Fand three months' imprisonment. The
OL,14,Fsentence was reduced by 25 per cent
OL,15,Ffrom seven years to account for his
OL,16,Fearly guilty plea.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
