OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782751677
OL,3,CTwo jailed after fraudulent refunds
OL,4,Cworth half-a-million uncovered
OL,6,FCampion was also sentenced to one year
OL,7,Fand nine months' imprisonment for one
OL,8,Fcount of theft and four counts of
OL,9,Ffraud and perverting the course of
OL,10,Fjustice.
OL,12,FSEROCU said confiscation proceedings
OL,13,Fwill now get underway to recover
OL,14,Fassets seized from Tourino. He has
OL,15,Falso been issued with a Serious Crime
OL,16,FPrevention Order, following his
OL,17,Frelease from prison.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
