PN,38806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782751677
OL,3,CTwo jailed after fraudulent refunds
OL,4,Cworth half-a-million uncovered
OL,6,FSenior Investigating Officer,
OL,7,FDetective Inspector Rob Havelock of
OL,8,FSEROCU's Economic Crime Unit, said:
OL,9,F"This sentence is a result of a
OL,10,Flengthy and complex investigation,
OL,11,Fdemonstrating the hard work and
OL,12,Ftenacity of our teams.
OL,14,F"The investigation team worked
OL,15,Fdiligently, over a short period, to
OL,16,Fobtain CCTV from across the country as
OL,17,Fwell as securing digital and financial
OL,18,Fevidence, which ultimately led to us
OL,19,Fsecuring criminal charges against
OL,20,FTourino.
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782751677
OL,3,CTwo jailed after fraudulent refunds
OL,4,Cworth half-a-million uncovered
OL,6,F"Forensic accounting showed that a
OL,7,Ftotal of #462,000 was obtained via
OL,8,Ffraudulent refunds and laundered
OL,9,Fbetween November 2023 and November
OL,10,F2025. Tourino, then used these funds
OL,11,Fto purchase high value goods and live
OL,12,Fa lifestyle he otherwise could not
OL,13,Fafford.
OL,15,F"Tourino and Campion may have thought
OL,16,Fthey could get away with it, but our
OL,17,Finvestigators stuck to the trail of
OL,18,Fthe money and uncovered a series of
OL,19,Fbank accounts, set up via a network of
OL,20,Fmoney mules, for the purposes of
OL,21,Flayering the stolen funds.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
