PN,38808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782751677
OL,3,CTwo jailed after fraudulent refunds
OL,4,Cworth half-a-million uncovered
OL,6,F"I hope this sends a clear message:
OL,7,Fanyone involved in this kind of scam,
OL,8,For trying to cheat the financial
OL,9,Fsystem, will be brought to justice."
OL,11,FAnyone with concerns about financial
OL,12,Fcrime or money laundering can contact
OL,13,FPolice on 101 or report it online.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@dO]
